Secure Code Practices: Ensured all Angular components and services adhere to secure coding practices, minimizing vulnerabilities and protecting user data.
Compliance with Accessibility Standards: Developed UI components in compliance with accessibility standards (e.g., WCAG), ensuring inclusivity and reducing legal risks.
Regular Code Reviews: Conducted thorough code reviews to identify and mitigate potential security risks, ensuring the integrity and reliability of the application.
Data Handling Policies: Implemented robust data handling and validation mechanisms in the UI, ensuring compliance with data protection regulations and safeguarding user information.
Proactive Issue Resolution: Actively identified and resolved UI-related risks and issues early in the development process, maintaining high standards of quality and performance.
